content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.34 - Gross weight of aircraft using Kennedy International Airport restricted

State Regulations

No aircraft on a dual tandem gear having an actual
gross weight of over 335,000 pounds including passengers, cargo, fuel, equipment, etc. shall land, take off or taxi at Kennedy International Airport
without permission. Notes
